data.description: HOME IS READY FOR YOU!! Spacious three bedroom and two and half bath home with numerous upgrades throughout and over 1900 square feet of living space.  Kitchen features granite countertops with stainless steel appliances and tile flooring. Family room, dining room and living room all feature laminate wood flooring with updated fixtures throughout. Remodeled bathrooms featuring a primary ensuite with a custom tiled shower, flooring, vanity and fixtures.  Time to come take a look at your next home and be home to enjoy the front porch and large backyard, including the playset, for the summer!!
